Seeing as how I've been here since the start, and earned my own gear (and good stuff for my level, too). All I really want is a chain bridle, and I fail to see how this disrupts anything. (I am fairly certain I could afford a chain bridle, had I stuck with one character and gotten high level rather than exploring different in-character personas, but I'm not angry or anything... finding out who I wanted to be was a huge part of the fun of FV.)<br>
