FV was very much worth coming to when I had to work from scratch. And it was the most fun I've ever had, reminding me of EQ's release... never felt so good to have a suit of chainmail... ::looks irritated:: I DID value that dream, and still don't see things your way.<br>
<br>
Note: I'm not making any offers to trade with anyone, just expressing my feelings on why I still don't quite understand.<br>
